MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2017-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 13th March, 2017
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 13th March, 2017:
(i)
Shri Manohar Parrikar relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Defence.
(ii)
Shri Arun Jaitley assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Defence. He will
continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Finance; and the office of
the Minister of Corporate Affairs.
